ZH: 爸爸是我的心腹，他对我非常关心。
EN: My father is my confidant, he cares about me a lot.

ZH: 她是我的心腹朋友，我对她无话不谈。
EN: She is my close friend, I can talk to her about anything.

ZH: 我的心腹是妈妈，她是我最亲密的人。
EN: My confidant is my mom, she is the closest person to me.

ZH: 他是我的心腹助手，帮我处理很多事务。
EN: He is my trusted assistant, helping me with many tasks.

